title: *PATREON PREVIEW* The Afters with Luke Fracher
description:
On our new weekly lightning round mini ep with Luke Fracher, we’re fucking around with personal style, Round Two, used underwear, dogs, last meals on earth, home-cooked meals, tattoos, designer vs. streetwear fashion, the best cities to shop in and more.
 
For more Throwing Fits, check us out on Patreon: www.patreon.com/throwingfits.
